title: Addenda to Thackery T Lambshead Guide to Diseases
description:
A tribute to the original book, The Thackery T. Lambshead Pocket Guide to Eccentric & Discredited Diseases (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Thackery_T._Lambshead_Pocket_Guide_to_Eccentric_%26_Discredited_Diseases).

Taken from yaddlezap.com/lambshead and turned into PDF. Authored by Jordan Inman. Featuring four new entries, Hyperectopic Pregnancy, Reverse Invisible Man Syndrome, Latent Chest Face Usurpation (Zola's Disorder), and Optiognosis!
